OL,3,CStarmer urges Travelodge boss to
OL,4,Cengage with MPs after meeting cancelled
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fwritten to Travelodge's chief
OL,8,Fexecutive urging her to "seriously
OL,9,Fengage" with the Government after she
OL,10,Fcancelled a meeting with MPs.
OL,12,FSir Keir said he was "very concerned"
OL,13,Fsome MPs did not hear from Jo Boydell
OL,14,Fdirectly, adding it is "incredibly
OL,15,Fimportant" lessons are learned after
OL,16,Fan "utterly appalling" sexual assault
OL,17,Fat one of the chain's hotels.
