OL,3,CStarmer urges Travelodge boss to
OL,4,Cengage with MPs after meeting cancelled
OL,6,FA guest at a Travelodge in Maidenhead,
OL,7,FBerkshire, was sexually assaulted by a
OL,8,Fman who had been given a key card to
OL,9,Fher room.
OL,11,FKyran Smith was jailed in February for
OL,12,Fseven-and-a-half years following the
OL,13,Fattack in December 2022.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
