PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774534301
OL,3,CStarmer urges Travelodge boss to
OL,4,Cengage with MPs after meeting cancelled
OL,6,FIn his letter to Ms Boydell, the Prime
OL,7,FMinister said: "I welcome your recent
OL,8,Fmeeting with several Members of
OL,9,FParliament, including the minister for
OL,10,Fsafeguarding and violence against
OL,11,Fwomen and girls, and the minister for
OL,12,Fvictims and tackling violence against
OL,13,Fwomen and girls (VAWG).
OL,15,F"I was, however, very concerned that
OL,16,Fsome MPs were not able to hear from
OL,17,Fyou directly.
OL,26,@oD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
