PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774534301
OL,3,CStarmer urges Travelodge boss to
OL,4,Cengage with MPs after meeting cancelled
OL,6,F"I urge you to seriously engage with
OL,7,FMPs and my Government to address the
OL,8,Fconcerns that remain around best
OL,9,Fpractice interventions for prevention,
OL,10,Fthe training being made available and
OL,11,Fthe pace of Travelodge's response."
OL,13,FReferring to the assault, he added:
OL,14,F"It is incredibly important that
OL,15,Flessons are learned and action is
OL,16,Ftaken to better protect guests."
OL,18,FMs Boydell apologised to the victim in
OL,19,Fa statement earlier in March, adding
OL,20,Fthe company had made changes to its
OL,21,Fdoor key policy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]vD@AOUxD@`O]
