PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774534301
OL,3,CStarmer urges Travelodge boss to
OL,4,Cengage with MPs after meeting cancelled
OL,6,FSmith, from Staines, Surrey, had lied
OL,7,Fto reception staff, telling them he
OL,8,Fwas the victim's boyfriend.
OL,10,FThe woman said staff told her Smith
OL,11,Fhad passed their security checks by
OL,12,Fproviding her name.
OL,14,FThe Government published its VAWG
OL,15,Fstrategy in December, with the aim of
OL,16,Fhalving this type of violence in a
OL,17,Fdecade.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
