PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1774534301
OL,3,CStarmer urges Travelodge boss to
OL,4,Cengage with MPs after meeting cancelled
OL,6,FIn the letter, the Prime Minister
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a personal mission for
OL,8,Fme: no woman or girl should feel
OL,9,Funsafe in this country, or fear for
OL,10,Ftheir life.
OL,12,F"VAWG is a national emergency and, as
OL,13,Fsuch, demands that all of us take
OL,14,Faction to tackle it."
OL,16,FIt is understood Travelodge has
OL,17,Flaunched an independent investigation
OL,18,Finto its room security policies.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUvD@UO]
